17:46:40.104 [INFO] This is a small knowledge-to-output repo template for an aspiring AI engineer - John

17:46:40.104 [INFO] ## Current shape

17:46:40.104 [INFO] This starter repo clusters around three loops:

17:46:40.104 [INFO] - distill research and conversations into cards + threads
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - turn those distilled notes into project outputs
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - use RFCs for bigger shifts in agent workflow or storage design

17:46:40.104 [INFO] That means the repo behaves more like a knowledge-to-output pipeline than a passive archive.

17:46:40.104 [INFO] ## Essentials

17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `01_capture` - keep canonical captured sources here
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `02_distill/` is the main operating surface: small cards in a flat folder, grouped by lightweight topic threads.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `04_projects/` holds concrete outputs that ship or get handed off.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `07_rfcs/` is for larger design changes that need a clearer argument before implementation.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `90_memory/` is the control center for how an agent works in the repo.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `99_process/` keeps the repo processes. Inspect that folder instead of relying on a catalogue here.

17:46:40.104 [INFO] ## What was removed

17:46:40.104 [INFO] - Almost all real content.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - Current project payloads, captures, newsletters, and course material.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - PoCs, images, and tool-specific experiments that were active recently but are not required to understand the operating model.

17:46:40.104 [INFO] ## Included folders

17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `00_inbox/` for unprocessed drops.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `01_capture/` for canonical captured source material in repo format.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `02_distill/cards/` for distilled notes.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `02_distill/threads/` for topic-level retrieval surfaces.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `04_projects/` for deliverables.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `07_rfcs/` for proposals.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `90_memory/` for agent memory and constraints.
17:46:40.104 [INFO] - `99_process/` for lightweight SOPs.

